import Hero from "./Hero"
import Highlights from "./Highlights"
import Testimonials from "./Testimonials"
import About from './About'

function Main(){
    return(
        <main>
            <Hero></Hero>
            <Highlights></Highlights>
            <Testimonials></Testimonials>
            <About id='About-Section'></About>
        </main>
    )
}

export default Main
